    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A vertical column of divine fire roars down from the heavens in a location you specify. Each creature in a 10-foot-radius, 40-foot-high cylinder centered on a point within range must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes [[/damage 4d6 fire]] damage and [[/damage 4d6 radiant]] damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>*Upcasting</strong>: Increase damage by either [[/damage 1d6 fire]] or [[/damage 1d6 radiant]] (your choice) for each spell level above 5th.</p></div></div>",
